  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1261020/extras/35ce7607d43e61b937503954ac467c0b.poster.avif?t=1630180887\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1261020/extras/35ce7607d43e61b937503954ac467c0b.webm?t=1630180887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1261020/extras/35ce7607d43e61b937503954ac467c0b.mp4?t=1630180887\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Edge of Dreams is a first person action with roguelike elements. You are the lone survivor in this strange space station. Shoot, explore, kill guards, create builds from items and skills, DIE, and repeat.<br><br><strong>FEATURES:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>ACTION</strong> with elements of roguelike.<br></li><li>Unlock new <strong>CLASSES</strong>, each with their own <strong>ABILITIES</strong>.<br></li><li><strong>RANDOM GENERATED</strong> locations for <strong>EXPLORE</strong> and <strong>ACTION</strong>.<br></li><li><strong>SKILL</strong> system for <strong>REPLAYABILITY</strong> and <strong>FUN</strong> play.<br></li><li>Unlock over 50 <strong>MODULES</strong>, that give different effects.<br></li><li>Use <strong>ARTEFACTS</strong> system for change game <strong>RULES</strong>.</li></ul>",
